title: King of the Roaring 20's: The Story of Arnold Rothstein (1961)
description:
King of the Roaring 20's: The Story of Arnold Rothstein (1961) 



The story of flamboyant Prohibition-era gangster, gambler and bootlegger Arnold Rothstein. 


Director:Joseph M. Newman 
Writers:Leo Katcher (book), Jo Swerling 
Stars:David Janssen, Dianne Foster, Jack Carson 


Story:'

Moving from one scam to another Arnold Rothstein quickly becomes rich, and settles into the life of owning big-town gambling joints. Along the way he falls in loves and marries, makes a life-long enemy of a cop on the take, and gradually becomes hardened even to his closest friends. Written by Jeremy Perkins.
